com.spnlangagent.langagent

Class RequestLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.spnlangagent.langagent.RequestLog

  • public class RequestLog
extends java.lang.Object
    Request Log object that stores a request URL and various metrics for the specific request. Similar to insight's request/RequestAggregator.
